// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0357 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 4b71b36b-b819-55a5-b62c-3c405174db9a

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*")
